snippet.title: [GOTY 2012 #5] Best VGM 1268 - Legend of Grimrock - Main Theme
snippet.description:
Composer humming the main theme: http://www.grimrock.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Stakula-humming-Grimrock-melody-07-09-2011.mp3

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC
Legend of Grimrock (2012)
Main Theme
Stakula
